Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.49,1:05:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始骨架…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.74,1:05:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部呼叫Σ01
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.16,1:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.49,1:05:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IKF的反應陸續消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.14,1:05:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.97,1:05:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體擅自動起來了
